{
  "texts": [
    "This evolution will necessitate ongoing exploration of learner interactions and characteristics to effectively promote dynamic personalization (Shemshack et al., 2021; Tetzlaff et al., 2021).",
    "For Research Question 3 (RQ3), students generally regarded ChatGPT as a valuable tool for facilitating personalized learning.",
    "The tutor bot's capacity to provide instant feedback and tailored guidance significantly aided students in understanding complex concepts and maintaining engagement with the learning material (Chang et al., 2023).",
    "Many students appreciated the interactive nature of the conversations, which enhanced their interest and motivation to learn.",
    "The study found that students valued the personalized support offered by ChatGPT, particularly its ability to scaffold learning by breaking down interactions into manageable steps."
  ]
}